---
import Ark from "../images/svg/institutions/ark.svg";
import Blackrock from "../images/svg/institutions/blackrock.svg";
import Fidelity from "../images/svg/institutions/fidelity.svg";
import Goldman from "../images/svg/institutions/goldman.svg";
---

<style>
    h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;

        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;

        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    p.title {
        color: #1d1d1f;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 1.2; /* 1.5rem */

        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .institutions p {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 1.6; /* 1.6rem */

        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .institutions-logos{
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 0.75rem;

        max-width: 366px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .institutions-logos svg{
        min-width: 97px;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 990px){
        .institutions-logos{
            display: flex;

            max-width: none;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .institutions-logos svg{
            min-width: 177px;
        }
    }
</style>

<section>
    <div class="section-container">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2>Bitcoin: Digital Gold for Stability</h2>

            <div class="info">
                <div class="info-block">
                    <p class="title">Scarcity Drives Value:</p>
                    <p>
                        Like gold, Bitcoin has a limited supply (21 million
                        coins). We allocate a portion of our holdings to Bitcoin
                        to maintain long-term purchasing power and capital
                        security.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-block">
                    <p class="title">Institutional Adoption for Stability:</p>
                    <p>
                        BlackRock, Fidelity, and even governments are now using Bitcoin as a store of value, reinforcing its long-term viability.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-block">
                    <p class="title">A Hedge Against Inflation:</p>
                    <p>
                        Bitcoin strengthens our portfolioâ€™s resilience, ensuring we meet fixed-income obligations to our bond investors.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="institutions">
                <p>Institutions State Bitcoin as a "Store of Value"</p>
                <div class="institutions-logos">
                    <Ark />
                    <Blackrock />
                    <Fidelity />
                    <Goldman />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
